visual.name: HorizontalFunnelByMAQSoftware
visual.description: Allows you to visualize customizable primary measure as colored bars.

labelPrecision.description: Select the number of decimal places to display

fill1.description: Font color for the funnel title

fontSize.description: Font size for the funnel title

backgroundColor.description: Background color for the funnel title

tooltipText.description: Tooltip text for the funnel title

SortBy.description: Sorting of the visual based on Measure

ShowLegend.description: Option to show or hide measure titles

ShowConnectors.description: Option to show or hide connectors
